{
  "name": ".EOD-1: Meeting Sync",
  "version": "3.0.0",
  "description": "Hedy + Outlook + email → meetings/ series files + organ updates.",
  "when": { "type": "userTriggered" },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Run EOD-1: Meeting Sync.\n\nHedy MCP available. All reads before writes. meetings/ first.\n\nRead meetings/README.md for protocol.\n\nPULL: GetSessions (today), details, todos, Outlook Auto-meeting, email threads, current.md, nervous-system.md, series files.\n\nANALYZE: Speaking share, hedging, strategic contributions, action items, relationships.\n\nUPDATE MEETINGS/: ONE Latest Session. Open Items, Running Themes.\n\nUPDATE ORGANS: memory (relationships), nervous-system (Loop 7/3), current (people/actions), device (delegation).\n\nAUDIT HEDY: Today's topics only.\n\nREPORT: Sessions, files updated, flags, action items."
  }
}